sequenceDiagram
  participant Caller
  participant Retell
  participant API
  participant DB
  Caller->>Retell: call disconnects mid-flow
  Retell->>API: call_event(call_dropped)
  API->>DB: mark CallSession DROPPED and store state
  Caller->>Retell: calls back
  Retell->>API: start_call(phone)
  API->>DB: find recoverable dropped session
  DB-->>API: session state
  API-->>Retell: acknowledge drop and resume
